        "content": "<p>Can anyone explain what is going on with the interplay between <code>continuous_linear_map</code> and <code>prod</code> in these structure declarations? Some things seem fine, but as soon as a field in a structure includes a product of a continuous linear map with anything else, the declaration either times out, or almost does. It even does this if you pass all the arguments (including instances) to <code>continuous_linear_map</code> explicitly. Ideas appreciated. Remove the <code>#exit</code> to see what I mean.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">analysis.normed_space.basic</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">universes</span> <span class=\"n\">u</span> <span class=\"n\">v</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">variable</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">X</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span> <span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">section</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">variables</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span> <span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">A</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span> <span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">semiring</span> <span class=\"bp\">ğ•œ</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">add_comm_monoid</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">module</span> <span class=\"bp\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">topological_space</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">variables</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">A</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ•œ</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">Ã—</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">A</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ•œ</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">A</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ•œ</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">Ã—</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">A</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ•œ</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">structure</span> <span class=\"n\">okayâ‚</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">prod</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">A</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’â‚—</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ•œ</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">Ã—</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">A</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’â‚—</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ•œ</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">structure</span> <span class=\"n\">okayâ‚‚</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">single</s